<i>adverb</i>: 현명히 [현명히], 똑똑히 [똑또키] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>현명히 [현명히]</dt><br>
<dd>wisely; sensibly</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 너그럽고 슬기로우며 일의 이치에 밝게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being benevolent, wise, and sensible.</dd><br>
<dt>똑똑히 [똑또키]</dt><br>
<dd>1. definitely; explicitly</dd><br>
<dd>분명하고 확실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Clearly and distinctly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cleverly; sensibly</dd><br>
<dd>머리가 좋고 영리하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Intelligently and wisely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>